              "displayName": "Eric Yang",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "In the current implementation, there is one control implemented.  The structure of the protocol is leading by number one, and follow by a JSON string, for example, sending heartbeat looks like:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n1{}\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThis is used to ping server to check if there is any output.  We can use the same format to set terminal size:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n1{cols:80, rows:25}\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThe rest of the data stream are treated as byte array.",
